videos.headline: Louisiana Monroe gets on the board first
videos.description: Brian Williams makes a one-handed grab in the back of the end zone for a 20-yard touchdown catch.

videos.headline: Texas State answers with a TD run
videos.description: Damian Williams muscles his way into the end zone for a one-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Louisiana Monroe's defense scores on defensive PAT
videos.description: Texas State goes for two and Caleb Tucker intercepts James Sherman's pass, returning it  for a defensive PAT.

videos.headline: Evans and Brown connect for big play
videos.description: Caleb Evans throws a strike to  Xavier Brown for a 64-yard catch.

videos.headline: Texas State pulls within 3
videos.description: Tyler Watts'  25-yard touchdown catch cuts Texas State's deficit to 16-13.

videos.headline: Texas State takes lead with trick play
videos.description: Hutch White finds a wide open Anthony J. Taylor for a 47-yard touchdown catch.

videos.headline: Louisiana Monroe retakes lead
videos.description: RJ Turner's 34-yard touchdown catch and run puts Louisiana Monroe back on top in the second quarter.

videos.headline: Luckett pounds it in for TD run
videos.description: Ben Luckett gets into the end zone with a 1-yard touchdown run to give Louisiana Monroe a 16-6 lead.

videos.headline: Louisiana Monroe forces game's first turnover
videos.description: LaMon Wesley Thompson recovers a fumble by Damian Williams  and returns it six yards to Texas State's 13-yard line.

videos.headline: Evans dances his way into the end zone
videos.description: Louisiana Monroe quarterback Caleb Evans makes one defender miss as he runs for a 10-yard touchdown run.

videos.headline: Williams scores Texas State's first second-half TD
videos.description: Texas State quarterback, Damian Williams keeps it himself for a 3-yard touchdown run.

videos.headline: Green breaks free for TD catch and run
videos.description: Marcus Green spins away from a defender for a 67-yard touchdown.
